OL,3,CBus driver killed pedestrian crossing
OL,4,Croad while reading piece of paper
OL,6,FA former Plymouth bus driver has been
OL,7,Fjailed for killing a pedestrian he
OL,8,Fmowed down while reading.
OL,10,FSimon Mumford, 54, from Ladysmith Road
OL,11,Fin Plymouth, was driving a single
OL,12,Fdecker City Bus through Plymouth on
OL,13,FSunday 7 January this year.
OL,15,FAround 6.20pm that evening, Mumford
OL,16,Fwas travelling along Western Approach
OL,17,Ftowards the traffic light controlled
OL,18,Fpedestrian crossing situated by the
OL,19,FSainsbury's store vehicle entrance.
