OL,3,CBus driver killed pedestrian crossing
OL,4,Croad while reading piece of paper
OL,6,FThe traffic light controlled
OL,7,Fpedestrian crossing was on red. At the
OL,8,Ftime Mumford had a piece of paper in
OL,9,Fhis hand and is seen on bus CCTV
OL,10,Flowering his glasses, looking down and
OL,11,Freading the paper for four seconds.
OL,13,FDuring this time he failed to see
OL,14,FAmallia Elmasry crossing the road in
OL,15,Ffront of him.
OL,17,FMrs Elmasry crossed the road when the
OL,18,Flights changed from red to amber and
OL,19,Fwas hit the bus.
OL,21,FMumford immediately stopped the bus.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
