OL,3,CBus driver killed pedestrian crossing
OL,4,Croad while reading piece of paper
OL,6,FMrs Elmasry died at the scene due to
OL,7,Fcatastrophic injuries.
OL,9,FMumford was sentenced at Plymouth
OL,10,FCrown Court on Thursday 12 December
OL,11,Fhaving pleaded guilty to causing death
OL,12,Fby dangerous driving at a previous
OL,13,Fhearing.
OL,15,FHe was jailed for two years and
OL,16,Fdisqualified from driving for six
OL,17,Fyears. He must sit an extended retest
OL,18,Fbefore he regains his licence.
