OL,3,CBus driver killed pedestrian crossing
OL,4,Croad while reading piece of paper
OL,6,FPolice sergeant Samantha Pullen from
OL,7,FDevon and Cornwall Police's serious
OL,8,Fcollisions investigations team said:
OL,9,F"This is a tragic case which again
OL,10,Fdemonstrates that even relatively
OL,11,Fbrief periods of distraction on the
OL,12,Froad can have fatal consequences.
OL,14,F"There is no doubt Simon Mumford did
OL,15,Fnot intend to take a life that day,
OL,16,Fbut by taking his eyes off the road to
OL,17,Fread the piece of paper, he did not
OL,18,Fspot Amallia Elmasry crossing, leading
OL,19,Fto the collision that resulted in her
OL,20,Ftragic death.
