OL,6,F"We'd like to express our sincere
OL,7,Fcondolences to Mrs Elmasry's family
OL,8,Fand remind motorists that regardless
OL,9,Fof what vehicle they drive, they must
OL,10,Fremain focussed on the road at all
OL,11,Ftimes to ensure the safety of
OL,12,Fthemselves and others."
